## ğŸ“¥ 1. Information We Collect

### 1.1 Account Information
- Username  
- Display name  
- Profile photo (optional)  
- Phone or email (if used for verification)

### 1.2 Messages & Media
- All messages/media are **end-to-end encrypted**  
- We **cannot** read your messages  
- Delivered messages are **immediately deleted**  
- Undelivered messages may be stored for up to **30 days**

### 1.3 Device & Technical Data
- IP address  
- Device type & OS version  
- Crash logs  
- App version & diagnostics  

### 1.4 Usage Data
- Feature interactions  
- Session duration  
- Device performance metrics  

### 1.5 Optional Permissions
- Contacts (never stored)  
- Camera, microphone, photos  
- Notifications  

